parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "Slurm",
"details": {
"script_name": "video2tator",
"slurm_options": {
"job_name": "video2tator",
"ntasks": 1,
"cpus_per_task": 32,
"mem_per_cpu": "2GB",
"time": "6:00:00",
"mail_type": "ALL",
"partition": "compute",
"output": "slogs/video2tator/%j.%x.txt"
},
"modules": [
"ffmpeg",
"gcc/8.5.0"
],
"virtual_environment": "venv",
"python_package": "tator",
"python_command": "python3 -m tator.transcode",
"tator_config": {
"token_file": "tator_token.txt",
"host": "https://tator.whoi.edu",
"project_id": 1,
"media_id": 1,
"work_dir": "tator_transcode_workspace"
},
"input": "$1 (VIDEO_FILE)",
"output": "transcoded video uploaded to Tator",
"other": {
"umask": 000,
"logging": "echo \"Job ID: $SLURM_JOB_ID, JobName: $SLURM_JOB_NAME\"\nhostname; pwd; date",
"time_tracking": "time python3 -m tator.transcode ...\nTZ=UTC0 printf '%(%H:%M:%S)T\n' $SECONDS"
}
}
}
```
